  "detailed_description": "<h1>Take a vacation and solve mystery on the island! 🐠🌴</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/2467f3badfdaad675b09f1c339efae86.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>Start from a street food cart and build an established cafe in the most unlikely place: A deserted beach bordering a popular tourist beach in a remote island far to the south! Convince both the tourists and locals to come at your establishment and make them loving it. But that's not at all, the island have its own stories waiting to unfold, depending on your choice!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.poster.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.webm?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.mp4?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features:</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Develop your cooking skills and specialize on cooking certain type of dish or just master all of them.<br></li><li>Manage the delicious and enticing food and drinks you are going to serve to the island's prospective customer.<br></li><li>Design and decorate your cafe with various decorations to cater to the increasing taste of your clientele.<br></li><li>Interact with your customers, reject outrageous demand or find the middle ground? Your choice!<br></li><li>Discover the story of the island!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.poster.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.webm?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.mp4?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/2467f3badfdaad675b09f1c339efae86.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>Start from a street food cart and build an established cafe in the most unlikely place: A deserted beach bordering a popular tourist beach in a remote island far to the south! Convince both the tourists and locals to come at your establishment and make them loving it. But that's not at all, the island have its own stories waiting to unfold, depending on your choice!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.poster.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.webm?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/aade629d58d6dfe3263b225f1ae387a6.mp4?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Key Features:</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Develop your cooking skills and specialize on cooking certain type of dish or just master all of them.<br></li><li>Manage the delicious and enticing food and drinks you are going to serve to the island's prospective customer.<br></li><li>Design and decorate your cafe with various decorations to cater to the increasing taste of your clientele.<br></li><li>Interact with your customers, reject outrageous demand or find the middle ground? Your choice!<br></li><li>Discover the story of the island!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.poster.avif?t=1604545488\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.webm?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1398080/extras/9bd3587fe491dc727d98dd9a26d6084f.mp4?t=1604545488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
